msgid "Spiritual Seekers and Mystics"
msgstr "Ceisio Gwaed a Mystigau"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Curious, introspective, open-minded, and drawn to "
"esoteric knowledge. They may have a strong interest in uncovering hidden "
"meanings or patterns in life. Occupations: Spiritual coaches, tarot readers,"
" astrologers, or individuals involved in New Age practices. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to lean toward spiritual or metaphysical beliefs. They may "
"see the tools as a way to connect with deeper truths or universal energies."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personalr: Rhyfeddol, introspectif, agorwr meddwl, a dymunol i "
"ddysgu gwybodaeth esoterig. Efallai eu bod yn ddiddordeb mewn canfod "
"ysgafnau cudd neu drafodaeth o drafodaeth o'r bywyd. Cyflogaeth: Mae "
"rhaglenwyr spiritig, darllenwyr tarot, astrolwyr, neu unigolion sy'n ymyredu"
" mewn arferion New Age. Spectrum Ideologig: Yn debyg i ymarferion spiritig "
"neu metafrasyddol. Gallant weld y teclynnau fel ffordd o gysylltu gyda "
"gwirioneddau ddiffuant neu ysgafnau universaol."

msgid "Numerologists and Gematria Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Numeroloedd a Gwaedwyr Gematria"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Analytical, detail-oriented, and fascinated by the "
"relationship between numbers and language. They may enjoy decoding symbolic "
"meanings. Occupations: Freelance numerologists, writers on esoteric topics, "
"or hobbyists exploring numerology. Ideological Spectrum: May range from "
"those who view numerology as a fun intellectual exercise to those who "
"believe in its profound spiritual significance."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Analydd, canranol, a ddiddordebwyd yn y berthynas rhwng "
"rhifau a iaith. Efallai eu bod yn mwynhau dad-dadlau difiniadau symbolaidd. "
"Cyflogaeth: Numeroloedd hyffordd ar-lein, ysgrifennu ar bynciau esoterig, "
"neu hunangynnu'r raddio'n gwob. Spectrum Ideologig: Efallai i'r rhai sy'n "
"gweld numeroleg fel gêm ddysgu a'r rhai sy'n credu yn ei chlydysg spiritig "
"pwysicaf."

msgid "Historians and Linguists"
msgstr "Hanesyddion a Llenyddion"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Scholarly, methodical, and interested in historical or "
"cultural contexts of numerical systems like Abjad. Occupations: Academics, "
"researchers, or students studying Middle Eastern languages, history, or "
"religious texts. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools from a "
"secular, academic perspective, focusing on their historical or linguistic "
"significance."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Arolwg, a methodolig, a ddiddordeb mewn cyd-destunau "
"hanesyddol neu ddiwylliannol o systemau rhifol fel Abjad. Cyflogaeth: "
"Academics, ymchwilwyr, neu studiaethion sy'n astudio iaith Mewnion Dwr "
"Cenedlaethol, hanes, neu destunau crefyddol. Spectrum Ideologig: Deunyddion "
"i'w fwrw ymlaen o'r safle seculr, arolwg, gan sylchu ei chlydysg hanesyddol "
"neu iaith."

msgid "Religious or Faith-Based Individuals"
msgstr "Personau crefyddol neu ddibynol ar Gofio"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Devout, reflective, and seeking deeper connections to "
"their faith. They may use the tools to explore religious texts or divine "
"messages. Occupations: Religious scholars, imams, priests, or laypeople with"
" a strong interest in their faith’s mystical traditions. Ideological "
"Spectrum: Likely to have a traditional or conservative worldview, using the "
"tools to reinforce their spiritual beliefs."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Dymunol, reflektiv, a chwiliol cysylltiadau mwy dwfn i'w "
"gredo. Gallant ddefnyddio'r offeri i archwilio destunau crefyddol neu "
"negeseuon divin. Cyflogaeth: Gwybodaeth crefyddol, imams, piri, neu bobl "
"ymyrrwy gyda ddiddordeb yn ddwys i ddiddordeb a ddynaboeth y gredo. Spectrum"
" Ideologig: Deunyddion i'w fwrw ymlaen o'r safle tradcywnol, arolwg, a "
"chroeni at y gredo spiritig."

msgid "Writers and Artists"
msgstr "Ysgrifennwyr a Sgyrff"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Creative, imaginative, and drawn to symbolic or abstract"
" concepts. They may use the tools for inspiration or to add layers of "
"meaning to their work. Occupations: Authors, poets, visual artists, or "
"musicians. Ideological Spectrum: May range from secular creatives to those "
"with a spiritual or mystical bent."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Greadigol, ymddiddorol, a dymunol i sgiliau symbolaidd neu"
" darluniau. Efallai i'r offeri ymyrru i'r dylanwad neu ychwanegu llwybr i'r "
"ddenu. Cyflogaeth: Awdur, poet, deithryn a sgyrff, neu wredydd. Spectrum "
"Ideologig: Efallai i'r rhai sy'n seculr i'r rhai sydd â ddyrn spiritig neu "
"mystig."

msgid "Puzzle and Riddle Enthusiasts"
msgstr "Pwysau a Gwaedwyr Riddle"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Playful, intellectually curious, and enjoy solving "
"complex problems or decoding patterns. Occupations: Hobbyists, puzzle "
"designers, or educators. Ideological Spectrum: Likely to approach the tools "
"as a form of entertainment or mental exercise, with little ideological "
"attachment."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Chwaraegol, ddiddordebol, a mwynhau datrys problemau "
"cymhleth neu ddad-dadlau patrwmau. Cyflogaeth: HOBBYIST, ddelwerion puzzle, "
"neu addysgwr. Spectrum Ideologig: Deunyddion i'r offeri fel ffurf o gêm neu "
"hyffordd i'r meddwl, gyda llai o gysylltiadau ideologig."

msgid "Conspiracy Theorists and Alternative Thinkers"
msgstr "Teoriadau Conspiracy a Myfyrwyr Allweddol"

msgid ""
"Personality Traits: Skeptical of mainstream narratives, drawn to uncovering "
"hidden truths or patterns in systems. Occupations: Independent researchers, "
"bloggers, or activists. Ideological Spectrum: May have a more radical or "
"unconventional worldview, using the tools to support alternative theories or"
" narratives."
msgstr ""
"Priodau Personol: Skeptical o'r narratives mwyaf, a dymunol i ddogfennu "
"gwirioneddau cudd neu patrwmau mewn systemau. Cyflogaeth: Ymchwilwyr "
"annibynnol, bloggeri, neu awdurdodion. Spectrum Ideologig: Efallai i'r rhai "
"sydd yn debygol o'r worldview radikal neu allweddol, gan ddefnyddio'r offeri"
" i gefnogi teoriadau allweddol neu narrativeni."

